ariablelist"><dl class="variablelist"><dt><span class="term"><em class="parameter"><code>x</code></em></span></dt><dd><p>
                    Specify the first value to compare.
                </p></dd><dt><span class="term"><em class="parameter"><code>y</code></em></span></dt><dd><p>
                    Specify the second value to compare.
                </p></dd></dl></div></div><div class="refsect1"><a id="description"></a><h2>Description</h2><p>
            <code class="function">max</code> returns the maximum of the two parameters. It
            returns <em class="parameter"><code>y</code></em> if <em class="parameter"><code>y</code></em> is greater than
            <em class="parameter"><code>x</code></em>, otherwise it returns <em class="parameter"><code>x</code></em>.
